@page
@model AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<h2>About</h2>
<p>
    This is a sample ASP.NET Core 8.0 application that demonstrates the modernization 
    of a legacy ASP.NET Framework 3.0 application to a modern cloud-ready application.
</p>
<p>
    The application demonstrates:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>ASP.NET Core Razor Pages</li>
    <li>Modern authentication with Cookie Authentication middleware</li>
    <li>Azure App Service deployment</li>
    <li>Infrastructure as Code with Bicep</li>
</ul>
<p>
    This application maintains the same functionality as the original ASP.NET Framework 3.0 application
    while providing all the benefits of modern ASP.NET Core.
</p>
